    {
      "kind" : "parameters",
      "parameters" : [
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "The maximum amount of time the test may run for.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name" : "timeLimit"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content" : [
        {
          "anchor" : "return-value",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Return Value",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "An instance of ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.testing\/documentation\/Testing\/TimeLimitTrait",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : ".",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    },
    {
      "content" : [
        {
          "anchor" : "discussion",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Discussion",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Test timeouts do not support high-precision, arbitrarily short durations",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "due to variability in testing environments. You express the duration in",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "minutes, with a minimum duration of one minute.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "When you associate this trait with a test, that test must complete within",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "a time limit of, at most, ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "timeLimit",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : ". If the test runs longer, the",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "testing library records a",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "doc:\/\/org.swift.testing\/documentation\/Testing\/Issue\/Kind-swift.enum\/timeLimitExceeded(timeLimitComponents:)",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " issue, which it",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "treats as a test failure.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The testing library can use a shorter time limit than that specified by",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "timeLimit",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " if you configure it to enforce a maximum per-test limit. When",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "you configure a maximum per-test limit, the time limit of the test this",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "trait is applied to is the shorter of ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "timeLimit",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " and the maximum per-test",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "limit. For information on configuring maximum per-test limits, consult the",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "documentation for the tool you use to run your tests.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If a test is parameterized, this time limit is applied to each of its",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "test cases individually. If a test has more than one time limit associated",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "with it, the testing library uses the shortest time limit.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If you apply this trait to a test suite, then it sets the time limit for",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "each test in the suite, or each test case in parameterized tests in the",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "suite.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "For example, if a suite contains five tests and you apply a time limit trait",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "with a duration of one minute, then each test in the suite may run for up to",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "one minute.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind" : "content"
    }
  ],
